## Quickstart

```bash
# Install dependencies (uv handles the venv).
uv sync

# Copy + edit secrets.
cp .env.example .env
$EDITOR .env

# Database
uv run python manage.py migrate
uv run python manage.py createsuperuser

# Serve
{%- if bakery.container_setup != 'none' %}
docker compose -f compose.local.yml up --build
{%- else %}
just serve
{%- endif %}
```

Then open <http://localhost:8000>{% if bakery.use_mailpit %}, or <http://localhost:8025> for Mailpit{% endif %}{% if bakery.api_layer == 'ninja' %}, or <http://localhost:8000/api/docs> for the OpenAPI UI{% endif %}.

